data_table.description: Pulmonary Function Test Diffusion, Generation 3 Exam 2, New Offspring Spouse Exam 2, and Omni 2 Exam 2. Subjects performed two maneuvers to measure diffusion capacity. If the first two maneuvers were not acceptable and reproducible, a third maneuver was performed. Only maneuvers that met acceptability criteria (based on inspired volume, breath hold time, and rapidity of expiration, per ATS/ERS guidelines) were retained in this dataset.
